pageContext.claim: “Many, many of the great auto companies are coming back into Michigan. They're coming back into Pennsylvania, Ohio, Florida, North Carolina.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump often claims that car plants are being built in several swing states he would need to win reelection in 2020. Although some automakers have announced new plants or expansions in Michigan, Ohio and South Carolina, there's little or no evidence for the other swing states Trump mentions.
